ts cards are polished, displaying title, category, description, and link with clear visual cues. I'm focusing on responsiveness and visual consistency. I am also working on adding a \"build\" section with different solutions.\n\n\n\n**Adding New Solutions**\n\nI am now focusing on expanding the content by adding entries such as real-time commerce recommendations, telecom operations optimization, and agentic customer support. I am adding AI solutions for digital-first retail brands, including a \"Build AI GCC (Global Capability Center)\" entry, with details and relevant keywords. I am working on adding \"Financial Services & Trust\" for regulated teams to improve the database.\n\n\n\n**Expanding Industry Focus**\n\nI'm now expanding the dataset to include \"Health & Life Sciences\" and \"Public Service & Education\" entries. I've added respective descriptions, categories, and keywords. I am working to ensure precise and relevant search results in the new industry sectors.\n\n\n**Expanding Public Service Data**\n\nI'm now expanding the database by incorporating detailed entries on Public Service & Education. I'm focusing on keywords like \"civic,\" \"grant,\" and \"university,\" with descriptive entries. I am also working on adding \"Consumer & Digital Industry,\" including \"retail\" and \"telecom\" keywords. I'm focusing on mapping these sectors into the defined structure.\n\n\n**Adding Governance & Agents**\n\nI'm now expanding \"Capabilities\" with entries for \"Agentic AI\" and \"AI Governance,\" adding relevant keywords like \"autonomous,\" \"compliance,\" and \"guardrails.\" I've also incorporated the \"AI Labs\" entry to foster collaborative innovation. I want to build out related search results and optimize for related keywords.\n\n\n**Updating Keyword Strategies**\n\nI am currently updating the \"Capabilities\" section with an \"AI Operations\" entry, focusing on automating monitoring and deployment. I've enriched \"AI Labs\" to encompass terms like \"co-innovate\" and \"sandbox\". I am also focusing on ensuring optimal results for related keywords.\n\n\n\n**Refining Resource Categorization**\n\nI'm now refining the resource categorization. I've added more detail to the articles, videos, podcasts, and reports entries, including relevant keywords to improve search results. I've incorporated new entries like \"Build AI with GFF,\" adding links to further enhance the database. I'm focusing on ensuring clear search results.\n\n\n**Refining Database Details**\n\nI'm now enriching the dataset with more interactive details and considering additional fields. I've focused on ensuring clickable example searches function seamlessly, including \"Build AI for Banking,\" \"Create University AI Lab,\" \"Insurance AI,\" and \"Mining AI\". I'm also ensuring the links are correct, and all data provides perfect results.\n\n\n**Implementing Search Refinement**\n\nI'm now implementing the search component's core functionality, including state management for the input and results. I am focusing on building the filtering logic for real-time results, based on title, category, description, and keywords. I am working to define the various states with custom prompts for empty and no-results scenarios. I want to build a truly robust search solution.\n\n\\n\\n\n\n\n**Implementing Interactive Search**\n\nI'm now implementing interactive features like instant query clearing (the 'X' button) and example query setting. I'm leveraging Framer Motion for smooth animations and elegant results transitions. After verifying and re-reading the file, I'm ready to completely replace `QuickSearchSection.tsx` with a new, fully typed component.\n\n\n"}}
